This repository includes a modified version of MatCal (matcalFast.m),
originally written by Lougheed, B.C. & Obrochta, S.P. (2016, 2019) and
also licensed under CC BY 4.0. The original source is available at:
https://github.com/bryanlougheed/MatCal

Calibration curve data files (.14c) in Functions/CalCurves/ were copied
from MatCal.
